title: MINDSET AND MACHINERY: How to Double Your Confidence to Win Big, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO269
itunes:title: MINDSET AND MACHINERY: How to Double Your Confidence to Win Big, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO269
description: I love history & when I was in high school, I wrote a paper on World War 2 fighter planes. The undisputed champion of all those fighter planes was the North American P-51 Mustang. In this episode, I use that plane & the brave pilots who flew it to explain how you can double your confidence when it comes to winning big at everything you do in business & in all of life.
